---
title: Coconut-Chilli Chicken with Sweet Potato and Black Bean Jumble
description: The marinade on the chicken provides a great sweetness to this dish that works perfectly alongside the heat from the fajita seasoning. All ready in the shake of a mariachi band's maracas..
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mango-marinated-chicken-7863f4e3-5b1bd5b4.jpg
